item.description: SoftLayer_Product_Item_Tax_Category Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Product_Item_Tax_Category data type contains the tax categories that are associated with products. Local id An internal identifier for each tax category. Type: integer keyName The key name of the tax category. Type: string name The name of the tax category. Type: string statusFlag The status of the tax category. Type: integer
